      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a reliable, no-frills daily driver. While the engine and transmission are fully functional and the car is roadworthy, it shows clear signs of age including some cosmetic wear on the interior and minor scratches on the exterior. It has been maintained to stay operational, but a new owner should expect to address some minor fluid leaks and aging suspension components in the near future.",
