      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since day one! We're talking a spotless interior, gleaming paint, and a ride that's as smooth as silk. It's been tucked away in a garage and treated with nothing but love. If you\u2019ve been searching for that perfect, 'like-new' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Let's chat and get you into the driver's seat!",
