    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S represents a peak-condition example of the 996.2 chassis, featuring the iconic Turbo-width bodywork and the 3.6L M96.03 flat-six engine. The powertrain is enhanced by VarioCam Plus technology and has been meticulously maintained, including a proactive IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, delivering power through a sophisticated viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system. The suspension remains taut with factory-spec Bilstein damping, while the braking system utilizes four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors for exceptional thermal management. This vehicle is mechanically flawless, with no bore scoring or fluid leaks, presented in showroom-state Arctic Silver over a Supple Leather interior.",
